	(3,1,'75006','Umbrella Academy','Famille. Super. Névrosée.','A dysfunctional family of superheroes comes together to solve the mystery of their father\'s death, the threat of the apocalypse and more.','80186863.jpg',0,'https://www.netflix.com/title/80186863','2019-02-15','2019-10-08 11:19:38','2019-10-08 11:19:38',NULL),
	(4,1,'1418','The Big Bang Theory',NULL,'The sitcom is centered on five characters living in Pasadena, California: roommates Leonard Hofstadter and Sheldon Cooper; Penny, a waitress and aspiring actress who lives across the hall; and Leonard and Sheldon\'s equally geeky and socially awkward friends and co-workers, mechanical engineer Howard Wolowitz and astrophysicist Raj Koothrappali. The geekiness and intellect of the four guys is contrasted for comic effect with Penny\'s social skills and common sense.','70143830.jpg',0,'http://www.cbs.com/shows/big_bang_theory/','2007-09-24','2006-08-23 17:34:38','2006-08-23 17:34:38',NULL),
	(5,4,'64165','Dix pour cent',NULL,'At a top Paris talent firm, agents scramble to keep their star clients happy—and their business afloat—after an unexpected crisis.','80133335.jpg',0,NULL,'2015-10-14','2008-07-16 20:23:16','2008-07-16 20:23:16',NULL),
	(6,1,'62650','Chicago Med','Ils entrent en scène quand la crise frappe.','An emotional thrill ride through the day-to-day chaos of the city\'s most explosive hospital and the courageous team of doctors who hold it together. They will tackle unique new cases inspired by topical events, forging fiery relationships in the pulse-pounding pandemonium of the emergency room.','80061157.jpg',0,'http://www.nbc.com/chicago-med','2015-11-17','2019-07-08 08:05:00','2019-07-08 08:05:00',NULL);
